  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  primary cancer

          -  right-side located tumor (from cecum to proximal transverse colon)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  tumor with obstruction

          -  tumor with perforation

          -  clinically advanced tumor (T4 stage)

          -  tumor with distant metastases

          -  synchronous tumor
